tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE warehouse_capacity (
    warehouse_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    warehouse_name VARCHAR(255),
    capacity INT,
    utilization FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE warehouse_capacity (
    warehouse_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    capacity INT,
    utilization INT
)

CREATE TABLE warehouse_inventory (
    warehouse_id INT,
    product_id INT,
    quantity INT,
    PRIMARY KEY (warehouse_id, product_id)
)

CREATE TABLE warehouse_history (
    warehouse_id INT,
    snapshot_date DATE,
    capacity_used INT,
    utilization_percent FLOAT,
    PRIMARY KEY (warehouse_id, snapshot_date)
)

CREATE TABLE warehouse_alerts (
    alert_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    warehouse_id INT,
    alert_type VARCHAR(50),
    alert_message TEXT
)
